{"type":"message","id":"cda5263b","parentId":"5f135e16","timestamp":"2026-03-08T00:01:37.456Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"成功了！现在我需要把文档链接发给用户。让我用message工具发送。","thinkingSignature":"08d64aae0202df3ed2813e3aa50789d88f6b9e01ea68884ff46de9a2ccb33319"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ye9o2ck2k1gd_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"📚 今日股市学习内容已整理完毕！\n\n**第9天：K线形态学习**\n主题：锤子线、上吊线、吞没形态、晨星暮星\n\n文档包含：\n✅ 四个关键K线形态的详细讲解\n✅ 形态特征、技术含义、操作建议\n✅ 相关导读链接（书籍+网站）\n✅ 股市传奇故事：尼古拉斯·达瓦斯的箱体理论\n✅ 实战练习建议\n\n🔗 https://feishu.cn/docx/Wa7BdtjdhoI9HcxZzkNcVOSvnjf"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":3996,"output":171,"cacheRead":14461,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18628,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772928087270}}
