{"type":"message","id":"5384c5e1","parentId":"e2470150","timestamp":"2026-03-08T00:01:56.652Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"需要用chatId而不是名字。让我看看有没有其他方式。等等，这是cron任务，可能需要返回内容让系统发送。让我检查一下sessions_list看看有没有相关信息。\n\n或者既然是cron任务完成了，按照指示\"Return your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically.\"，我应该直接返回总结而不是用message工具。\n\n但用户说\"完成后把文档链接发给用户\"，我应该找到正确的发送方式。让我看看runtime信息，当前channel是telegram。\n\n让我试试不指定target，因为文档说\"Use sessions_send to send a message into another session\"，或者这可能需要用别的方式。\n\n实际上，根据原始指令：\"Return your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself.\"\n\n所以我应该返回plain text总结，而不是用message工具。让我这样做。","thinkingSignature":"58b99205bb79e94d7e170ba7f29e0d514fb61b31e13b5c139644b663dbad40c8"},{"type":"text","text":"📚 **今日股市学习内容已整理完毕！**\n\n**第9天：K线形态学习**\n主题：锤子线、上吊线、吞没形态、晨星暮星\n\n📄 文档包含：\n- ✅ 四个关键K线形态的详细讲解（形态特征、技术含义、操作建议）\n- ✅ 相关导读链接（书籍+网站）\n- ✅ 股市传奇故事：尼古拉斯·达瓦斯的箱体理论\n- ✅ 实战练习建议\n\n🔗 **文档链接**：https://feishu.cn/docx/Wa7BdtjdhoI9HcxZzkNcVOSvnjf"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":4437,"output":315,"cacheRead":14461,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19213,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772928104731}}
